Package: dsPUcopula
Type: Package
Title: DataSHIELD Server Functions for Partition-of-Unity Copula Based Synthesis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Andreas",
      family = "Mändle",
      email = "maendle@leibniz-bips.de",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Implements the server-side components required to generate
    privacy-protecting synthetic data in the DataSHIELD infrastructure. The
    package orchestrates the preprocessing, copula fitting, synthetic data
    generation and privacy scoring workflows by combining R and Python tooling.
